{
  "page": "Maiden's Tower",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Maiden's Tower</b> is the easternmost of the seven slender towers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>. From a balcony on the tower, one can see the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">Giant's Lance</a>.  \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maiden%27s_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maiden%27s_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_Stone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alayne Stone\">Alayne Stone</a> has apartments in the Maiden's Tower; they are large and more lavish than the little bedchamber where she had lived when Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a> was alive.  She has her own dressing room and a privy of her own, and a balcony of carved white stone that looks off across the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As <a href=\"/index.php/Gretchel\" title=\"Gretchel\">Gretchel</a> is tending to the fire Alayne pads barefoot across the room and slips outside.  The stone is cold against her feet, and the wind is blowing fiercely, as it always does up there, but the view makes her forget all that for half a heartbeat.\n</p><p>Alyane has the Vale before her, its forests and rivers and fields all hazy in the morning light.  She thinks that the way the sun is hitting the mountains makes them look like solid gold.\n</p><p>The snow-clad summit of the <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">Giant's Lance</a> looms above her, an immensity of stone and ice that dwarfs the castle perched upon its shoulder.  Icicles twenty feet long drape the lip of the precipice where <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa%27s_Tears\" title=\"Alyssa&#39;s Tears\">Alyssa's Tears</a> fall in the summer.  A falcon soars above the frozen waterfall, blue wings spread wide against the morning sun.\n</p><p>She rests her hands on the carved stone balustrade and makes herself peer over the edge.  She can see Sky 600 feet below, and the stone steps carved into the mountain, the winding way that leads past Snow and Stone all the way down the valley floor.  She can see the towers and keeps of the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>, as small as a child’s toys.  Around the walls the hosts of the <a href=\"/index.php/Lords_Declarant\" title=\"Lords Declarant\">Lords Declarant</a> are stirring, emerging from their tents like ants from an anthill. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maiden%27s_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>So lovely.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_Stone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alayne Stone\">Alayne Stone</a>, contemplating the view from the balcony</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maiden%27s_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Alayne I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404021512\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 206/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8656/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1107/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 199/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 805/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    7.919      1 -total\n 68.80%    5.448      2 Template:Ref\n 43.88%    3.475      2 Template:Ref/core\n 26.51%    2.099      1 Template:Quote\n 20.23%    1.602      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:12808-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404021512 and revision id 230010\n -->\n",
